tyle=\"color: red;\">「誰能幹就誰幹」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"誰能幹就幹誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"幹誰就幹撚誰"},{"pid":"f045fa0085afda3dd0bcf7e7a4a7ba45b4423b7d","tid":2028653,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳？<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"fdce2baf12ef075e384ff07f9dc92133f52dcc34","tid":2028653,"uid":38821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老味有咩咁能幹呀.<br />\n全部無視法律/程序夾硬黎, 有人夠膽反對示威就搵槍炮對付.<br />\n講到尾咪即係香港玩完, 你亦都無辦法再用香港搵著數, 一拍兩散.<br />\n整死香港呢隻會生金蛋既雞攬炒就叫能幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講香港人真係未撚驚過.<br />\n我們過去大半年上得街都有心理準備唔係比人打就比人拉.<br />\n一早有不成功便成仁既心理質素, 捱下窮算得乜. <br />\n仲可以順便比班中立我討厭政治撚感受下共產人人平等既鐵拳.<br />\n你地支那人試下食樹皮丫, 我就真係食住花生睇真暴動喇."},{"pid":"f7dee9f5fa0fb5c1ab0d594bbed6f8bd75d4a4c9","tid":2028653,"uid":276465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想睇下邊個笑到最後"},{"pid":"38bf4eed2221ab32edefa26033e5477282fe60a3","tid":2028653,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b6602d7c07bc110cfe3c371889761e8cfdf3590","tid":2028653,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會須對全國人民負責<br />\n真癲唔係扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60ae97e2a3ffcdaec9f54a055df79a42e27743f","tid":2028653,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"誰能幹就誰幹.............<br />\n真係能幹嘅都移左民啦"},{"pid":"8f5f15479123cc0e8de8eb29292b4da54f9d798d","tid":2028653,"uid":37111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"172e6899c7fe78190dcb0c2d99531f801d566ff8","tid":2028653,"uid":17459,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「誰能幹就誰幹」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:19:42.000Z","msg":"誰能幹就幹掉誰"},{"pid":"cc974629879500026f57d058b6b853cff6a29497","tid":2028653,"uid":119408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09bdf8276194e57189c8b314b3690dfef9727106","tid":2028653,"uid":283070,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"cf337cb89d5b32b7eb6d9bdea7be08f963dca5c4","tid":2028653,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳︰中央豁出去平香港亂局 不惜一切達到目的<br />\n22.05.2020 10:06<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳在一個電台節目表示，中央一直認為香港出現分離主義主張，是由於法律上不完備，因此由法律上著手是止暴制亂的重中之重，亦反映中央對香港能否於短期內自行立法毫無信心，令中央有急迫感和危機感，必須出手平息亂局，形容中央今次是豁出去，不惜一切要達到目的。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳又指，中央多年來不斷強調香港的高度自治權來自全國人大常委會，香港回歸20多年，已到了50年不變的中段，仍未能完成本地立法，全國人大常委會須對全國人民負責，不能不採取行動。他又說相信今次訂立的會是長期性法律，不會在日後本地自行就23條立法便失效，亦同時為本地23條立法訂下框架，條文不能與中央訂立的法律相牴觸。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，由近日中聯辦和港澳辦頻頻就香港事務發聲，以致現時港版國安法，都是一步步執行去年四中全會的決定，又相信中央的行動仍未結束，日後仍會出手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289310&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289310%26csid%3D261_341&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=dbcc8521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289310&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李克強：實行重點項目攻關「揭榜掛帥」<br />\n22.05.2020 09:56<br />\n<br />\n國務院總理李克強在政府工作報告說，要提高科技創新支撐能力，穩定支持基礎研究和應用基礎研究，加快建設國家實驗室，重組國家重點實驗室體系，發展為社會研發機構，深化國際科技合作，加強知識產權保護，實行重點項目攻關「揭榜掛帥」，「誰能幹就誰幹」。<br />\n<br />\n李克強說，當前和今後一個時間，中國發展面臨風險挑戰前所未有，但中國有特別政治和制度優勢、雄厚經濟基礎、巨大市場潛力，億萬人民勤勞智慧，只要直面挑戰，堅定發展信心，增強發展動力，維護和用好中國發展重要戰略機遇期，當前的難關一定能闖過，中國的發展必將充滿希望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289310&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289310%26csid%3D261_341&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=dbcc8521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289310&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"漏口佳真係保皇黨裡面最黑我憎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"港版胡叼盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eddda94b70407a530803373bd6ae6ac77208cc6","tid":2028653,"uid":319113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"誰能幹就幹誰"},{"pid":"270b7e606cb6bc1e39ecf59f56c6cc9c317160f7","tid":2028653,"uid":346722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a9852cc77dea9a3eac058073484cafe740b24a8","tid":2028653,"uid":173179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"172e6899c7fe78190dcb0c2d99531f801d566ff8","tid":2028653,"uid":17459,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「誰能幹就誰幹」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"你行你上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3941312bf391a644c960839e2f1b480684df4f9","tid":2028653,"uid":49316,"like":0,"disl